rly treatment of uncertainties can\nhave in traditional aerospace engineering practices. The results are presented\nand compared to those from a Gaussian Process regression performed on a single\ndata source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2019 17:52:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-13"}
