 computing service for scientific\ncomputing applications, which reduces cost by $5\\times$ compared to\nconventional cloud deployments and keeps performance overheads under $3\\%$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2019 21:58:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2020 19:34:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-18"}
