ween datasets and\nfeaturization/model types. AMPL is open source and available for download at\nhttp://github.com/ATOMconsortium/AMPL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Nov 2019 00:13:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 01:38:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-15"}
